org.schema.game.common.data.element

Class ElementCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.schema.game.common.data.element.ElementCollection

  • public abstract class ElementCollection
extends java.lang.Object
    An ElementCollection is used to manager all effects of blocks on an entity, ranging from weapons to power, shields, thrusters, scanners, everything.
